    {
        "content": "<p>Thanks for your answer! But I don't think it is a very natural way to do this. <span aria-label=\"thinking\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f914\" role=\"img\" title=\"thinking\">:thinking:</span></p>",
        "id": 522390063,
