    {
        "content": "<p>Let me clarify my goal: I want to strengthen the inductive hypothesis from <code>P n</code> for a fixed <code>n</code> to <code>∀ n &gt; 0, P n</code>.</p>",
        "id": 522392549,
        "sender_full_name": "Han Han",
        "timestamp": 1749051886
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Can you explain what that means? In <code>P n</code> the <code>n</code> is free, but in <code>∀ n &gt; 0, P n</code> the <code>n</code> is bound.</p>",
        "id": 522394233,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1749052353
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Sorry, I don't fully understand the distinction between free and bound variables—though that might be why the <code>generalizing</code> tactic failed. Mathematically, what I'm trying to do is generalize the inductive hypothesis from <code>P n</code> for a fixed <code>n</code> with <code>hn : n &gt; 0</code> to <code>∀ n &gt; 0, P n</code>.</p>",
        "id": 522396457,
        "sender_full_name": "Han Han",
        "timestamp": 1749052945
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I think this is a case where it's easier to prove something more general first:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">lemma</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">simple_aux</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hf</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">m</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hn</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">induction</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">with</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">zero</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hn</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">succ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Function</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">iterate_succ_apply'</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hf</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hn</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">lemma</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">simple</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℕ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hf</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hn</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">simple_aux</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hf</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hn</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
